/>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:03:15.000Z","msg":"所以咪問 有冇動機係咪主要考慮之一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:21:16.000Z","msg":"刑事案黎講動機係其中主要因素"},{"pid":"f29e5e05592e8a22e175668b22def2c163b6e230","tid":1031761,"uid":107405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:30:03.000Z","msg":"香港咁多年對危駕都係判得唔重 <br />\n講左好多年但從來唔見有修例加重刑罰<br />\n之前成日有的士佬超速撞死人 又修路工人 又收費亭職員 但全部審完出黎仲判得少過暴動罪個班<br />\n人命就係值咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0d9743c127da04c6b1f3ff2303a3a96746d6bc","tid":1031761,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:32:27.000Z","msg":"人命唔值錢亞洲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2a24d92b809c4d5f0748d774d6770a8b858fc9","tid":1031761,"uid":42879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:40:19.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔係咁老實，而係話自己突然暈左會唔會仲小啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b805dfbb1446530bed751cdeb6346d1a0af38e7a","tid":1031761,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:48:26.000Z","msg":"炒車死人真係太輕,雖然對方係支那蝗"},{"pid":"efb9e1f3fc5e39e2206f7ff4153546ea412f8714","tid":1031761,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:49:28.000Z","msg":"完全冇阻嚇力<br />\n難怪而家啲司機越黎越自私，唔將行人放在眼內<br />\n個個一見到斑馬線有人想過就篤油唔俾過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}